==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chandelier
<hw>Chan`de*lier"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Chandler</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A candlestick, lamp, stand,
gas fixture, or the like, having several branches; esp., one hanging
from the ceiling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Fort.)</fld> <def>A movable parapet, serving to
support fascines to cover pioneers.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>chandelle</ent>⟦br⟧
